us drive at the first stop sign continue on campus drive east and you will come to a 4 way stop sign at alvarado row continue past alvarado row and turn right into the first driveway into a parking lot which is the back of the haas center building visitor parking is available in parking structure 6 under wilbur field on campus drive parking the closest visitor parking is located in parking structure 6 the underground parking garage at wilbur and campus drive east visitor parking is only on the first level of the garage once you enter the structure veer right and drive toward the back wall all visitor slots are identified with a p visitor sign and a slot number a payment machine is at the back wall in front of the stairway elevator exit please exit using the stairway elevator near the payment machine the haas center is on campus drive and salvatierra walk approximately one block from this garage exit coming out of the garage turn left onto arguello and turn right onto campus drive east conference room reservation van reservation building safety and emergency information conference room reservation groups haas center for public service printer friendly version connect with us facebook facebook twitter twitter video icon video stanford seal newsletter giving to haas action logo support our work haas center for public service 562 salvatierra walk stanford ca 94305 650 723 0992 hours m f 8 5 support our work feedback copyright 2011 stanford university terms of use copyright complaints report a problem with this site
